      <title>英国财政大臣里夫斯详述“破碎不堪”的英国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/uk-chancellor-reeves-to-detail-a-broke-and-broken-britain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯将在周一的演讲中描绘英国公共财政的严峻形势，她将陷入反对党和本党内部批评者的夹缝之中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/uk-chancellor-reeves-to-detail-a-broke-and-broken-britain</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普承诺解雇 Gensler，选择“热爱”加密货币的监管者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/trump-pledges-to-fire-gensler-pick-regulators-who-love-crypto</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，如果他重返白宫，他将解雇美国证券交易委员会主席并选择对加密货币友好的监管机构，以吸引虚拟货币爱好者并利用该行业在政治舞台上日益增长的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/trump-pledges-to-fire-gensler-pick-regulators-who-love-crypto</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 21:21:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯测试“怪异”标签，抨击特朗普和万斯的言论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/harris-tests-out-weird-label-in-attack-on-trump-vance-rhetoric</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在总统乔·拜登退出总统竞选后的首次筹款活动中，称唐纳德·特朗普及其竞选搭档JD·万斯的言论“奇怪”，这一举动延续了她上任以来民主党人发起的攻击路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/harris-tests-out-weird-label-in-attack-on-trump-vance-rhetoric</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 20:18:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Priti Patel 参加英国保守党领袖竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/priti-patel-enters-crowded-leadership-race-for-uk-conservatives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前内政大臣普丽蒂·帕特尔 (Priti Patel) 于周六参加保守党党魁竞选，成为保守党在选举中遭遇史上最惨痛失败后决定党派方向的第五位候选人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/priti-patel-enters-crowded-leadership-race-for-uk-conservatives</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戈兰致命空袭威胁以色列将予以严厉报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/deadly-strike-in-golan-triggers-threat-of-harsh-israeli-payback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[戈兰高地发生火箭弹袭击，造成 11 名儿童死亡，20 多名儿童受伤，这引发了人们对以色列和黎巴嫩真主党武装组织之间战斗迅速升级的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/deadly-strike-in-golan-triggers-threat-of-harsh-israeli-payback</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 19:59:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安全局势减弱，几内亚军政府面临民主压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/pressure-builds-on-guinea-junta-for-democracy-as-security-wanes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几内亚军事领导层面临的压力与日俱增。近三年前，在两名民主活动人士失踪后，军事领导层夺取了政权，并举行了选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/pressure-builds-on-guinea-junta-for-democracy-as-security-wanes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 18:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戈兰高地遭袭后内塔尼亚胡将返回以色列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-27/ap-newsalert-israel-s-prime-minister-is-returning-home-as-quickly-as-possible-after-attack-in-the-golan-heights-his-office</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列特拉维夫（美联社）——以色列总理办公室称，戈兰高地遭受袭击后，总理将尽快回国。]]></description>
