      <title>乌克兰称其无人机在俄罗斯北极地区击中战略喷气式飞机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/ukraine-says-its-drones-hit-strategic-jet-in-russia-s-arctic</link>
